        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/12/77454259/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_1458217073664569688.png",
                "id": "talent84959",
                "key": "Gleaming Spear - Guardian Stance",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Gleaming Spear - Guardian Stance"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Attaches a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Heron Shield</span> to this character and <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepares Heron Strike.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Heron Shield</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p>While preparing this Skill: Grant 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Shield</span> points to the character to which this is attached.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Heron Strike</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>(Prepare for 1 turn)</p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/12/77454259/93ab629528ecee5857a14f427422bbb3_1387084353088754419.png",
                "id": "talent2935",
                "key": "Sacred Rite: Heron's Sanctum",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Sacred Rite: Heron's Sanctum"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span> and creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prayer of the Crimson Crown</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Prayer of the Crimson Crown</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span></p><p>Your characters' <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Normal Attacks</span> deal +1 DMG.</p><p>Your Sword, Claymore, and Polearm-wielding characters' <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> is converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After you switch characters</span>, you deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>. (Once per Round)<br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span>: <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">2</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/12/77454259/28ae761238404c68bd54c08344cb9c72_1652252836371797857.png",
                "id": "talent78662",
                "key": "Sacred Rite: Wagtail's Tide",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Sacred Rite: Wagtail's Tide"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Hydro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives +2 Physical or Pyro DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/12/77454259/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_7641039445106782813.png",
                "id": "talent93998",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Prepare Skill</span></strong></p><p>Some Skills cannot be used directly. Instead, they need to be <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepared</span> over a certain number of turns.<br>When it is a certain player's turn, and this player's active character is currently <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> a Skill, this player's turn will be skipped. If the Skill has finished being <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepared</span>, the character will directly use that Skill at this time. (Skills that require <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> cannot activate effects triggered by \"using a Skill\" or \"triggering an Elemental Reaction\" or other such effects.)<br>Only active characters can <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepare</span> Skills, and if an active character who is <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> a Skill gets switched off-field, their <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparation</span> will be interrupted.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Shield</span></strong></p><p>This Shield will be consumed to protect the character who equips it from DMG.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong></p><p>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds) </span>-1.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/12/77454259/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_4093885407474881550.png",
                "id": "talent65038",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
